snippet.title: RO2: Gate of the World - Alfheim F
snippet.description:
A familiar looking library in Alfheim, from RO2: Gate of the World, a game which has since been scrapped and replaced with RO2: Legend of the Second.

Yikes, that derpy translation pack.
